name: The Hall of Santuari
description: The Hall of Santuari was left empty by Sentinels after they start the Crystal of Matahari Campaign. A majority of the Santuarian population was deactivated and put into Cryonics to secure planet energy consumption. Self-assembling and self-repairing hall building from Santuari used to be the place for Sentinels and Santuarian sacred ceremonial occasions.
